metadata.name: Pop Posh 1
metadata.description:
This is an OG from my portfolio. If you've come to a pop up I'm at or visited my website, this is one of my fan favorite prints. It's kinda a big deal in Minnesota... *insert face palm*. I really just wanted to pick a piece that I still love and get it into as many hands as I can. It has been in my life a while and now I can price it for everyone to cop and add to their wallet! 

Enjoy the colors and swag of this piece. I created the lines of her shirt by hand digitally built the rest around her and the end result was a digital diva that is giving. 

- Eb
